            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> Cauti et Caut<lb break="no" n="2"/><expan><abbr>opat</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> Florius Florentius et <lb n="3"/>An<supplied reason="lost">c</supplied>arinius Severus nepos <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aeti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> Faus<supplied reason="lost">tino et Rufino</supplied> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift befindet sich unter einer Darstellung des Cautes. Obere Hälfte der Figur ergänzt; Angabe der Höhe schließt die Ergänzung mit ein. (B): CIMRM 1165: Z. 1/2: Caut/op(a)t(i); Mattern: Z. 1/2: Caut/op[a]t(i); Z. 3: n[e]pos.</p>
            </div>
